STATEMENT OF HON. DAVID VITTER, 

U.S. SENATOR FROM LOUISIANA 

Senator VITTER. Thank you, Madam Chair, and I look forward to 

the testimony, as well. 

The  specific  title  of  this  hearing  seems  to  be  ‘‘Market  Manipula-
