Mr.  GREENBERGER.  Oh,  well,  look,  NYMEX  says  that  because 
they  treat  investment  banks  and  hedge  funds  as  oil  dealers. 
They’re—— 

Senator DORGAN. And they are not. 
Mr.  GREENBERGER.  Yes.  Of  course  they’re  not.  Thirty  percent  of 

